This archive contains the NOVAe-specific part of Genode.

It also contains the source code of the NOVAe hypervisor in the src/kernel/nova/
directory.

This NOVAe version is maintained at 'https://github.com/alex-ab/NOVA.git'.

Please note that NOVAe has a license distinct from Genode. NOVAe's license can
be found at 'src/kernel/nova/LICENSE'.
